@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-4">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <div class="card p-4">
        <p class="lead">At [LinkBook], we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to ensure it is kept secure.</p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and billing information when you use our services. This information is necessary for account creation, processing payments, and improving our services.</p>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>The information we collect is used to provide you with better services, personalize your experience, and communicate with you about updates, promotions, and offers that may interest you. We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties without your consent.</p>

        <h3>3. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure. We use encryption and secure connections to ensure the safety of your data during transmission and storage.</p>

        <h3>4. Cookies</h3>
        <p>We use cookies to enhance your user experience by remembering your preferences and tracking usage patterns. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features of the website may not work properly without them.</p>

        <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. If you would like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].</p>

        <h3>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating this page and revising the effective date at the top.</p>

        <h3>7. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <address>
            [LinkBook]<br />
            [Central University of Technology, Free State
            Private Bag X20539
            BLOEMFONTEIN
            9300]<br />
            Email: [222002054@stud.cut.ac.za]<br />
            Phone: [+27 71 668 9191]
        </address>
    </div>
</div>
